    {
        "text": "Is that true?",
        "start": 33.06,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Uh, I'm not sure about any idiot but it is easy",
        "start": 34.22,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "and we're going to find out.",
        "start": 37.5,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "So what we want to do is we want to knock out",
